<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.5">
<l>vāṉat tiluḷḷīr valiyī ruḷḷīrē</l>
<l rend="indent">laṟaiyō vantuvāṅ kumiṉeṉ pavaṉpō</l>
<l>lēṉat turuvā kiyavī caṉentai</l>
<l rend="indent">yiṭava ṉeḻavāṅ kiyeṭut tamalai</l>
<l>kāṉak kaḷiyā ṉaitaṉkom piḻantu</l>
<l rend="indent">katuvāy matañcō rataṉkai yeṭuttuk</l>
<l>kūṉaṟ piṟaivēṇ ṭiyaṇṇān tuniṟkuṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that our father, supreme lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">having taken the form of a boar,</l>
<l>took and raised up [as if it was] a clod of dirt,</l>
<l rend="indent">as if saying “Heavenly residents!</l>
<l rend="indent">Why don’t you come and take [it] if you’re stong enough?”</l>
<l>called Govardana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where stood the rutting forest elepant,</l>
<l rend="indent">having lost its tusk, raised its trunk</l>
<l rend="indent">as it oozed the descending ichor,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] looked up longingly at the curbed crescent moon,</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
